in case we need it.

17:24.586 --> 17:25.628
- You'll need it.

17:25.670 --> 17:28.131
That hurricane is headed
straight for us.

17:28.173 --> 17:31.009
Mm-kay.
[elevator pad beeps]

17:37.891 --> 17:39.893
- I wanted to help my friend,

17:39.934 --> 17:43.313
