my immediate attention.

17:43.355 --> 17:45.565
I'm Detective Baltasar Peniche.
[knocks]

17:46.900 --> 17:47.984
Good morning, sir.

17:48.026 --> 17:49.736
I am Detective
Baltasar Peniche,

17:49.778 --> 17:50.945
