24:04.027 --> 24:05.612
- Alex?

24:07.655 --> 24:09.157
[grimaces]

24:09.908 --> 24:11.493
Alex?

24:19.584 --> 24:21.211
- Ah, fuck.

24:21.252 --> 24:27.175
