24:33.056 --> 24:34.599
[scoffs]

24:42.190 --> 24:44.025
- What is "pasaje"?

24:44.067 --> 24:46.194
- That one's important.

24:46.236 --> 24:47.445
I don't know why,

24:47.487 --> 24:49.197
but it must have been
important once

24:49.239 --> 24:51.032
'cause it's right there.

24:52.325 --> 24:54.661
This fucking thing.

24:54.703 --> 24:57.122
I'm thinking this mural
is actually more

24:57.163 --> 25:00.667
about the Oceana Vista's
memory, right?

25:00.709 --> 25:03.378
Not just my memory,
but the Oceana Vista's memory.

25:03.420 --> 25:05.505
- Two kids are missing.

25:05.547 --> 25:07.757
And you were the last one
to see them.

25:09.175 --> 25:11.136
- What?

25:11.177 --> 25:14.723
- They came to your room
last night.

25:14.764 --> 25:16.307
- No.
- Yes.

25:16.349 --> 25:18.810
- No.
That's not right.

25:20.228 --> 25:21.438
Wait, what?

25:21.479 --> 25:25.233
- What do you remember
from last night?

25:25.275 --> 25:27.694
- Uh, last night.

25:27.736 --> 25:30.822
You're really torturing me
with a question like that.

25:32.574 --> 25:34.451
What the fuck?

25:34.492 --> 25:36.828
Uh...

25:36.870 --> 25:38.621
We went dancing.
- Uh-huh.

25:38.663 --> 25:40.498
- It was the Christmas party.
- Yes.

25:40.540 --> 25:41.875
- Gotcha.
- What else?

25:41.916 --> 25:43.501
- Soy pasaje.
What?

25:43.543 --> 25:45.420
- Hey, Alex.
- What?

25:45.462 --> 25:47.380
- What do you remember?
- I don't know.

25:47.422 --> 25:48.381
- You don't know.
- What do you remember?

25:48.423 --> 25:52.385
- Okay.
Uh, okay, who is this?

25:52.427 --> 25:53.678
- Luna.
- Uh-huh.

25:53.720 --> 25:56.598
And this?
- Some guy with a hat?

25:56.639 --> 25:57.682
- Yeah, I guess.

25:57.724 --> 25:59.225
Um, who is this?

25:59.267 --> 26:01.394
- Oliver.
- And this?

26:01.436 --> 26:04.272
- That's you, dummy.
- Yeah, who am I?

26:05.482 --> 26:08.026
- Baltasar Peniche Frías,

26:08.068 --> 26:11.571
head of security
and my best friend.

26:12.447 --> 26:16.534
Everything is fine, man.
I'm really--I actually am okay.

26:20.872 --> 26:22.999
- Oh, man.

26:23.041 --> 26:26.753
Alex, who--who are these two?

26:28.713 --> 26:30.757
- That, I don't know.
- You don't know.

26:30.799 --> 26:34.177
What--what were you doing
in your car this morning?

26:34.219 --> 26:36.888
Because you had blood
on your hands.

26:36.930 --> 26:38.640
Where were you coming from?

26:40.225 --> 26:42.102
You don't know?
- I don't know.

26:42.143 --> 26:43.186
- Mm-hmm.

26:43.228 --> 26:46.564
* *

26:46.606 --> 26:49.109
Hey, look at me and listen.

26:49.150 --> 26:51.486
Yeah, these two
were at the party.

26:51.528 --> 26:53.238
