with them.

26:53.279 --> 26:54.364
- No.
- Yes.

26:54.406 --> 26:56.116
And then they ran
into your elevator

26:56.157 --> 26:57.450
and got off on your floor.

26:57.492 --> 26:59.452
And five minutes after that,
you did the same.

26:59.494 --> 27:04.207
So I need you to tell me
what happened next, please.

27:08.294 --> 27:10.463
- I'm calling bullshit.

27:10.505 --> 27:12.424
This is a fuck hunt.
- Fuck off.

27:12.465 --> 27:15.010
[indistinct muttering]

27:15.051 --> 27:17.554
What did you do, Alex?

27:17.595 --> 27:19.305
What did you do?
- What did I do?

27:19.347 --> 27:20.682
- I don't know.
What did you do?

27:20.724 --> 27:22.642
- Well, what did I do?
Tell me what the fuck I did!

27:22.684 --> 27:23.852
I'm telling you
I don't remember!

27:23.893 --> 27:25.353
- Try to remember something,
please.

27:25.395 --> 27:26.563
