up there--

27:28.064 --> 27:29.274
- There's nothing in here, man!
- Okay, try to remember.

27:29.315 --> 27:30.442
- It's empty!

27:30.483 --> 27:33.945
[tense music]

27:33.987 --> 27:35.530
Jesus!

27:37.073 --> 27:39.200
- What did you do, Alex?

27:41.661 --> 27:44.748
[skateboard wheels rattle]

27:49.002 --> 27:53.214
Wait, where--
where did you get that?

27:56.676 --> 27:58.720
- I've had this
since I was a kid.

27:58.762 --> 28:01.222
- No, you haven't.

28:04.100 --> 28:07.854
This is Sam's.
