28:07.896 --> 28:10.398
- Look the other way
one last time.

28:10.440 --> 28:12.359
You and me, this resort--

28:12.400 --> 28:14.611
this is the family
we always wanted, right?

28:14.652 --> 28:16.071
Right?

28:16.112 --> 28:17.238
The hurricane's gonna come.

28:17.280 --> 28:18.948
