30:16.983 --> 30:21.696
* *

30:21.738 --> 30:23.281
- Alex!

30:23.323 --> 30:30.413
* *

30:45.720 --> 30:48.848
- Is it the end
or the beginning?

30:48.890 --> 30:49.974
[inhales]

30:50.016 --> 30:56.940
* *

31:08.993 --> 31:10.412
