32:05.216 --> 32:08.470
- * That's said,
forget it *

32:08.511 --> 32:12.098
- My mind, my memory,
it's just an empty space,

32:12.140 --> 32:15.310
where I find myself
completely alone.

32:15.352 --> 32:18.855
- * No reason why you should
stay here lying to me *

32:18.897 --> 32:20.565
- Alone and afraid
that I can't remember

32:20.607 --> 32:23.526
any of the things you were
afraid I might have done.

32:23.568 --> 32:25.403
- * Don't say anymore,
just walk out the door *

32:25.445 --> 32:29.491
- You asked me if I remembered
the kids in my room.

32:29.532 --> 32:31.701
I tried to remember
myself as a kid

32:31.743 --> 32:34.079
falling in love
for the first time.

32:34.120 --> 32:38.124
But, um,
I can't remember a thing.

32:38.166 --> 32:41.628
- * Then you can thank me
for mine *

32:41.670 --> 32:43.213
- So if I can't remember love,

32:43.254 --> 32:45.548
then what's the point?

32:45.590 --> 32:49.969
- * That's said,
forget it *

32:50.011 --> 32:53.556
* *

32:53.598 --> 32:56.309
* If there was a word,
but magic's absurd *

32:56.351 --> 33:00.313
* I'd make
one dream come true *

33:00.355 --> 33:02.065
- Whatever did happen
last night,

33:02.107 --> 33:05.235
I hope that either everyone
can forgive me...

33:05.276 --> 33:07.487
- * But don't ever doubt
how I felt... *

33:07.529 --> 33:09.614
- Or forget me.

33:09.656 --> 33:10.990
- * About you *

33:11.032 --> 33:13.993
* *

33:14.035 --> 33:18.248
- * But thanks
for your time *

33:18.289 --> 33:19.833
* Then you can... *

33:19.874 --> 33:23.712
- Have you ever seen
the green ray?

33:23.753 --> 33:26.339
It's the first ray
of the rising sun.

33:26.381 --> 33:27.966
[thunder rumbles]

33:28.008 --> 33:30.593
