- I thought you two
would be gone by now.

34:17.599 --> 34:19.934
[thunder rumbles]

34:25.523 --> 34:29.110
- I have nowhere to go.

34:29.152 --> 34:31.112
- Me neither.

34:31.654 --> 34:33.281
- Me neither.

34:36.493 --> 34:37.744
What's that smell?

34:37.786 --> 34:40.622
[wind whooshing]

34:40.663 --> 34:43.708
[structures crashing,
shattering]

34:49.547 --> 34:51.508
- [screams]

34:51.549 --> 34:54.219
[wind whooshing]

34:54.260 --> 34:57.222
[uneasy music]

34:57.263 --> 35:04.187
* *

